his character very well.

143
00:08:29,630 --> 00:08:30,880
I'm really out of options.

144
00:08:30,890 --> 00:08:32,060
Only you can help me.

145
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:36,220
Alright.

146
00:08:36,300 --> 00:08:37,300
I promise you.

147
00:08:38,860 --> 00:08:39,740
Thank you.

148
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:51,860
I thought this trip
would only be the two of us,

149
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:52,840
