154
00:09:03,210 --> 00:09:04,340
You actually

155
00:09:04,340 --> 00:09:06,020
dared to take such risks for us.

156
00:09:06,570 --> 00:09:08,220
Actually, I trust Mr. Yan.

157
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,820
If we find him soon,

158
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:12,740
