165
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:27,540
Everyone is on edge.

166
00:09:27,780 --> 00:09:29,000
It's always good to be careful.

167
00:09:30,020 --> 00:09:31,460
You're quite thoughtful.

168
00:09:32,020 --> 00:09:34,180
The mansion is lucky to have you.

169
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:38,700
You...

170
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:40,580
You actually dared to do

171
00:09:40,700 --> 00:09:41,660
